reviewText: Havent purchased these but will because i've seen all them so many times know them by heart. I love this show so much I could Literally watch this show everyday.
While I was never a fan of SEINFELD....I think Julia-Louis Dreyfus is hilarious in this...was surprised to see Eric McCormack and Megan Mullally, I am a "Huge" WILL & GRACE fan.
It arrived on time and in excellent condition. I haven't watched them yet so I'm assuming they are in great condition. They are brand new.
